Rf'(0)=Lf'(0)
Rf'(0)=\lim_{h\rightarrow 0} {f(0+h)-f(0)\over h}=\lim_{h\rightarrow 0}{sin h-0\over h}=1
LRf'(0)=\lim_{h\rightarrow 0} {f(0-h)-f(0)\over -h}=\lim_{h\rightarrow 0}{-sin(-h)-0\over -h}=-1
Rf'(0)\ne Lf'(0)
